Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:46.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向这丑陋的世界轻声说“再见”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:54.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}用这对朱色翅膀掩去一切丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:06.43,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,000)}思念如附着的污渍般挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:10.93,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在这地球上生存着的人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:18.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人窒息般地紧紧相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:25.03,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凝视着镜中的另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:30.93,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了隐藏自己的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:38.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去刺伤那些温柔善良的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:44.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向这丑陋的世界轻声说“再见”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:50.53,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}朱色的翅膀轻盈地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:56.93,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}烈火般的热吻一次次重复着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:02:09.03,CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就用这最后一吻收敛起热情奔放的心
Dialogue: 2,0:22:24.64,0:22:31.13,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}太阳把热情的目光投向这边
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.34,0:22:36.53,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}真想好好享受这夏天 这阳光
Dialogue: 2,0:22:36.54,0:22:43.93,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天会发生什么令人激情澎湃的事吗
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.24,0:22:48.63,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}小小的不安点缀着这美妙的期盼
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.24,0:22:56.03,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,200)}夏天的回忆涌现在我脑际
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.14,0:23:01.93,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}晶亮的碎片注入天空大海充满世界
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.04,0:23:06.73,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,100)}低声私语请求你的拥抱
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.74,0:23:09.73,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}顽皮地挑逗
Dialogue: 2,0:23:09.74,0:23:14.73,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}不需要你做出暧昧的温柔
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.24,0:23:22.63,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,000)}那一瞬 我已经预感到一切
Dialogue: 2,0:23:22.64,0:23:26.53,C2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(000,300)}在这热情洋溢的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫光可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  光就是光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太高兴了  太喜欢  健还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个给人添麻烦的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是多么可爱的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给每个人添麻烦真是很够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要花钱  要照顾她  吃的  用的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实样子好像不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  算了  就随你喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正还很年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当拿好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  你看  有饭粒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己弄掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做些丢脸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我也会被人笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书包在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厕所  不要跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健  今天也要上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然的  因为是高中生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  后天  大后天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校好像很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  有趣或无趣  喜欢或讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界上能清楚分出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们也不用那么辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然健很笨  在某些地方却特别认真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱管闲事  因而有了不必要的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不否认  但还是不要对他昨天的话太期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那个有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是作为他青梅竹马的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健  既然说了要保护光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该给光十足的安全感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得她很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也打算做我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但学校和打工是不能偷懒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}第三话  两人的树阴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西瓜切好了 要吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在雨天望着外面很有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  在小时侯也有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对上年纪的女人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看下雨的理由就不只是有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 每个人都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西瓜切好了  快点去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常喜欢西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说  听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"出现了"...是说幽灵小偷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是六人份的手卷寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是特级的  特级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  我也想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要幻想了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说都有种紧迫感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我是相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我夏天的连衣裙被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是妹妹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  变态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  健可以每天吃到光做的早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还一起吃晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在我们面前吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我偏要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不甘心啊  我们没有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想和像光一样的可爱女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在同一间屋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还说喜...喜欢我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都在做这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说了  浅仓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光看就很痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  怎么可能做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊  你在犹豫什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把恋爱看成这么无所谓的事  健
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光所追求的东西并不是这个  肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊  健  可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  今天我不打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  我去跟叔叔说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  你还是第一次提这样的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去约会或者做其他事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约会是吗  也许是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约会  什么时候  什么地方  和谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢下雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 喜欢被雨淋湿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢闭上眼听雨声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和天空  水还有地面秘密的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果听的懂在说什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会更喜欢被雨淋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛  但是  你能懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前能懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那时一点都不觉得是很好听的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使知道这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只喜欢上了一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是讨厌下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚能看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去问他本人不就好了嘛  他就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  那样太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样特地去问他太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以  没关系的  那个虫只吃得下一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到夏天甲虫就会来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲虫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候到夏天  马上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但等段时间就会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话就很无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是想快点见到甲虫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有性急的甲虫就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想见你而稍微性急的甲虫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么时候来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有着白色和红色的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么都发着光  非常的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到也许再也看不到了  就变得非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许就是那个时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且之前的事也不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想再看看那个发光的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在这里的话  也许还能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  辽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我今天会迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以帮我和班主任说一声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  这不能成为迟到的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 快点送过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你所看到的  今天你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分钟就得回来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说勉强的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是为山中狩猎所准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近这里不是有暴风雨和小偷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都像是山上下来的野猪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野猪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投降吧  西瓜小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有看见过的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被它逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天又被甩了啊  健
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很啰嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只会说这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  辽  不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在健心中是从未体会过的痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚什么也没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前天也是  再之前也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天那个夜晚会再出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这里不是你该留的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里  你只是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你参观更多的地方和见更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的地方  快乐的地方吗  是好人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不见得是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见得只是快乐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不一定全是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像现在这样一定也不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有它在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在你身边的  那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克恩  是我取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克恩是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但克恩是很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要它  它需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看的那个白色和红色的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想那个红色就是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找它  你知道地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道  虽说知道但它只认同我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里就是明住的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那个池  一直在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这个扎了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吮吸了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你很容易受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没有好好的为你考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  因为是我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要注意的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择森林的也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是辽的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明真是坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 还是应该帮你准备鞋的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我会注意的走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不痛吗  我背你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的  这不什么都没发生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很担心  湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你照顾了它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它是我家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它果然还是想跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有它会很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的东西  重要的东西我有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多也不能代替丢失的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.03,0:23:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是二宫辽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让明看更多的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见各种各样的人  这是我的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么也想不到什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以什么理由都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:24:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  这个丑与美的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个森林什么时候都可以生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我知道那样也许比较好...
